Package com.toolrental.data

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CheckoutRequest
    CheckoutRequest is a bean class mainly with properties, setters and getters which contains a user request for a tool rental.
    RentalAgreement
    RentalAgreement is a bean class mainly with properties, setters and getters which contains the final output of ToolRentalManager.checkout().
    RentalCharges
    RentalCharges is a bean class mainly with properties, setters and getters which contains the immediate output of the pricing lookup in ToolRentalManager.checkout().
    Tool
    Tool is a bean class mainly with properties, setters and getters which contains the tool definitions.
    ToolCharge
    ToolCharge is a bean class mainly with properties, setters and getters which contains definitions for tool rental pricing.
